    "data": [
        {
            "title": "巴郡發行價值14億美元日圓債券 發行利差低於上次",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 巴郡周五發行2101億日圓（14億美元）的日圓債券，發行利差較上次發行有所下降。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次發行包括四個品種在美國證券交易委員會註冊的高級無抵押債券，期限從3年到15年不等，總募資額超過4月發行的的900億日圓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次發行中金額最多的3年期債券，定價較以TONA為基礎日圓互換利率中間價高出48個基點，上一次發行是70個基點。5年期債券的利差為64個基點，也低於上一次。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"柏克夏歷年發行日圓債券情況\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EAX5ODso1o8SJ7Yk5asP4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/ab99021847407d1c297efc641d0db324\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">柏克夏歷年發行日圓債券情況</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Resona資產管理首席基金經理Takashi Fujiwara表示，投資者對公司債券的需求近來復甦。他補充說，巴郡是備受歡迎的公司，其信用評級穩健，外國投資者在二級市場也十分活躍。他表示，利率上升重新激發了投資者對企業債券的需求，「投資者看到了更高的價值，日圓計價債券也在他們的考慮範圍之內」。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b83f2eb2-e1e5-335e-b3ca-bcfd0004a85a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Berkshire Hathaway Raises ¥210.1B from Multi-Tranche Bond Sale</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9F%8F%E5%85%8B%E5%A4%8F%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E5%83%B9%E5%80%BC14%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83%E7%9A%84%E6%97%A5%E5%9C%93%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8-%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E5%88%A9%E5%B7%AE%E4%BD%8E%E6%96%BC%E4%B8%8A%E6%AC%A1-063448344.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-14 20:10:53",
