        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經濟降溫</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國10月份經濟活動降溫程度超過預期，受投資低迷影響。同期房價跌幅加大，傳統的銷售旺季以疲軟的數據收官，近期的寬鬆措施未能提振低迷的市場。當月的信貸擴張表現亦創一年多以來最弱，受政府債券發行步伐放緩以及整體借貸需求低迷所拖累。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">疲態持續</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國前財政部長樓繼偉警告，國內房地產市場低迷將持續，並加劇通縮壓力，應推出更多刺激措施以為經濟提供緩衝。中國逾10億美元的房地產抵押貸款面臨違約風險，除非能夠達成展期或再融資協議。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-553ad835-077d-3387-a17e-b85f58ca7102-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">降息爭議</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">多位聯儲會官員近期就貨幣政策發表偏鷹派言論，對12月降息必要性提出質疑。交易員押注聯儲會12月降息可能性不足50%。不過，白宮國家經濟委員會主任哈塞特表示，目前掌握的經濟數據支持繼續降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">熊市格局</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受新一輪避險情緒和科技股拋售拖累，比特幣跌破10萬美元大關。曾經可靠的力量紛紛離場，令比特幣失去了支撐今年漲勢的一個重要支柱。10X Research的分析師稱，加密貨幣市場已進入確認的熊市格局。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">抽成15%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊控股與蘋果公司達成一項協議，將由蘋果負責處理微信小遊戲和小程序的支付，並抽成15%，由此解決了一項長期的爭端。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-043246675.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-14 14:25:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英國預算案風向突變 財政大臣考慮放棄增稅計畫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"英國預算案風向突變 財政大臣考慮放棄增稅計畫\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6tUgnv97CJNC.6U8ovdEBg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/a06c7720-b95f-11f0-a777-491225be69e6\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">英國預算案風向突變 財政大臣考慮放棄增稅計畫</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E6%A1%88%E9%A2%A8%E5%90%91%E7%AA%81%E8%AE%8A-%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E5%A2%9E%E7%A8%85%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB-005837852.html",
